relevant_findings.general: Alert, no acute distress, slow speech
relevant_findings.HEENT: Sclera anicteric, mucus membranes dry, oropharynx clear
relevant_findings.cardiovascular: tachycardic with regular rhythm, normal S1 + S2, no murmurs, rubs, or gallops
relevant_findings.lungs: Clear to auscultation bilaterally, no wheezes, rales, or ronchi

relevant_findings.extremities: warm, well perfused, 2+ pulses, no clubbing, cyanosis, or edema
